## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all possible strategies for identifying boundaries. The information is also subject to the limitations of the sources, which may not reflect the most recent research or diverse cultural perspectives. Additionally, the strategies discussed may need to be adapted to fit specific contexts or individual differences.